<section class="page-hero">
    <div class="page-hero-content">
        <h1>EVENTS & CAMPUS IMPACT</h1>
        <p>
            Driving technical excellence and community engagement through high-impact 
            competitions, challenges, and expert-led industry workshops.
        </p>
    </div>
</section>

<section class="events-section">
    <div class="events-container">
        <div class="events-grid">

            <div class="event-card">
                <div class="event-header">
                    <h2>ATV Racing</h2>
                    <span class="event-badge">APOGEE Flagship</span>
                </div>
                <p><strong>Overview:</strong> A highly successful off-road track event at APOGEE designed to test the limits of all-terrain vehicles.</p>
                <div class="event-stats">
                    <strong>Impact:</strong> Achieved 150+ pre-registrations and over 200 on-spot signups.
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="event-card">
                <div class="event-header">
                    <h2>Water Rocketry Challenge</h2>
                    <span class="event-badge">Competition</span>
                </div>
                <p><strong>Overview:</strong> An interactive technical challenge focused on crafting and launching rockets powered entirely by high-pressure water expulsion.</p>
                <div class="event-stats">
                    <strong>Impact:</strong> Drew an impressive crowd of over 150 participants.
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="event-card">
                <div class="event-header">
                    <h2>Industry Workshops</h2>
                    <span class="event-badge">Knowledge Session</span>
                </div>
                <p><strong>Overview:</strong> Hosted Dr. Piyush Desai, inventor of the world's most efficient electric motor, who provided profound insights into Industry 4.0.</p>
                <div class="event-stats">
                    <strong>Impact:</strong> Personally guided 50+ students across various campus tech teams.
                </div>
            </div>

        </div>

        <div class="impact-summary-card">
            <h3>OUR OVERALL REACH</h3>
            <p>
                We take pride in guiding over <strong>300+ students</strong> through technical workshops 
                and hosting <strong>500+ live participants</strong> across our APOGEE events.
            </p>
        </div>

    </div>
</section>
